Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.95,0:00:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.34,0:00:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.05,0:00:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.92,0:00:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.71,0:00:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天空盜賊 空盜團少年——酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.53,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邂逅了被稱為煌珠的武器種族少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並將其從長期的沉睡中喚醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.59,0:02:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當時來了一批自稱煌珠完全保護協會——守護翼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.93,0:02:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要保護少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.74,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同時還有別的刺客也是為了少女而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷為了保護少女而竭盡全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.05,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目睹這一切的少女決定以煌珠的力量幫助他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.35,0:02:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二唱 命運的同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.31,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這太厲害了 又輕得像羽毛一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是七煌寶樹之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,梅札蘭斯一族的最終血統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯的戰鬥能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽是聽說過 但沒想到這麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最後一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別以為會讓你們繼續為所欲為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去滅火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保護引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽我說 太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在不是說這話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也快去滅火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,滅火 難道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.22,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,休想得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.52,0:04:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.31,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞭解 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大 我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.89,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.51,0:04:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定會救你出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.33,0:04:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那小子 有點大人樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別愣著 快幹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.09,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放了那女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.22,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好有挑戰性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該是說 本能性地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓開 讓開 讓開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和預想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.83,0:05:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真纏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉不能帶上你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要在下面重新來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.79,0:06:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽好 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是值得自豪的紅山貓一員——酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是個男人的話無論發生什麼都要保護好那女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得到的話你就算是個大人了 懂了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再會了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 雖然這很不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但至少我們可以回守護翼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.73,0:06:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也很不幸地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才 這個輕輕地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:06:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,操縱桿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 那女孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.41,0:07:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道是 被那些傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以為你不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傷口 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這只是擦傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.27,0:07:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼涼的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.62,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來我還沒問你叫什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過叫我蕾好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道是不喜歡名字長長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過還是喜歡別人叫我酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.07,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請多指教 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因為我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首領他們也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大從沒騙過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.03,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分開的時候 老大說了再見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.53,0:08:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我相信一定會在某個地方再見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 你要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是我喚醒你的時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那安寧之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.52,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天空之上雲層之中 不為所見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有即為無 無即為有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,金壁輝煌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人們無憂無慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創造新的財富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奠定新的根基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾所說的煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傳說是科技高度發達的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.07,0:09:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遠在天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢幻般的樂園啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像很不錯的樣子 不過是第一次聽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.67,0:10:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去的話也許會搭上性命哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 好想去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不喜歡和我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要保護你到那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成為一個男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我們兩個人出發去煌珠樂園了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我們去守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.15,0:10:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有我們煌珠完全保護協會——守護翼在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了難處也請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.06,0:10:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護翼無論什麼都會微笑地快速解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於第一次同契的你們而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.28,0:10:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,內行的指導員會和藹可親地從最簡單的開始教起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用淺顯易懂的教材...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思破壞你說話的興致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那兩個人走了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼走了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你們又沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這難道不是一種緣份嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.13,0:11:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣 不一起去守護翼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說了不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們來帶路去煌珠樂園好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 我們是多麼的好心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.36,0:11:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想幹什麼 你們別跟過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.31,0:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量用得太多 該是睡覺的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睡覺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,簡單來說 算是充電時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.12,0:11:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 不是什麼身體不舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 一點都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是煌珠還有很多不可思議的地方哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.37,0:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更何況 花季少女的一些事你是一竅不通的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.04,0:12:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道不覺得既懂少女的心事\N又瞭解煌珠樂園的我是不可缺少的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會使壞的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.81,0:12:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子餓了 肚子餓了 肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再忍一會兒 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概再走一會兒就可以到城鎮或是鄉村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.68,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再一會兒到底是什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幾小時幾分幾秒幾個飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 別欺負我了 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在是要心平氣和忍耐的時候哦 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了那個有吃的地方的話會讓你吃個夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總部那裏拿來的錢還有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總部那裏拿來的錢還有很多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說了沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什...什...什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,離開總部的時候不是帶了那麼多的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼 錢是放哪兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那當然是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和飛船一起燒掉了 全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 什麼東西的燒烤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不不不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 吵吵鬧鬧的一幫傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.74,0:14:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過這麼吵都沒醒 很累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.91,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錢的話搶個劫什麼的不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之我正餓著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.99,0:14:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搶劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再怎麼沒錢我們也是守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們怎麼能和空盜團同流合污呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算錢沒了心靈也要一直保持純潔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太偉大了 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.37,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想保住小命的話就把錢交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.76,0:14:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是長鬃尾熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會出現在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.97,0:14:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後再想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼 可以吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 奇雅 冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,槍擊沒用 奇雅也正餓著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牽引之線{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼此傾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與我共頌念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,氣息相應{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纏繞飛旋之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠相隨{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赤誠之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纏繞飛揚之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.92,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.80,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好驚人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.59,0:16:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我睡了很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.15,0:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 這附近有沒有旅店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五個人吧 五個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也算上 如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 各位是守護翼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.40,0:16:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 想不到我們還挺有名的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家 請到我家來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.51,0:16:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也想表示一下救了我們的謝意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.31,0:16:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔 Thank you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃 這個很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.16,0:16:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼好招待的請慢慢享用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過好開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們勤勤懇懇地幹著這樸實的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連這麼普通的人也知道守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.03,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是看報紙還是怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是的 從報紙上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 你父親呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.54,0:17:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 有一點小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好吃的 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.79,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 本來就不怎麼吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 我可以拿過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.93,0:17:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 奇雅也太能吃了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃是人生最大的樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.70,0:18:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,適可而止啊 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇雅和龍威是夫妻嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.02,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是搭擋而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊是啊 搭擋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那kiss什麼的不做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼冒出來這麼一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的是 明明是個孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到挺早熟的嘛 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一般般吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷和蕾很像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是外貌上的而是氣質上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這...這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 感覺氣息一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相同的...空氣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩人是戀人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紅著臉好像挺開心的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.65,0:19:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因為...怎麼說呢...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.19,0:19:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 遇到蕾後我就掌握了巨大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.13,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前不久還沒件像樣的兵器的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下子就能戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然是很高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了是吧
